The '''Mungaka''' language is spoken by the people of [[Bali Nyonga]]. Bali Nyonga is located grasslands of [[Cameroon]] in the [[Northwest Province (Cameroon)|Northwest Province]]. They are the descendants of the [[Bali Chambas]] in Northern [[Nigeria]].
